chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/network/sent_bytes_count', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.description: Value can be greater than 100% on machine types that allow bursting
chart.name: CPU %
Disk I/O Bytes / min
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/read_bytes_count', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('instance/disk/write_bytes_count', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU % Trend
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/cpu/utilization').scale(100).publish(label='A')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (A).max().publish(label='F', enable=False)

chart.description: Delta of bytes written/read to disk
chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/write_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('instance/disk/read_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')
